pullsbody: Inhuman ads infrastructure was decommissioned almost a year ago. this change removes all functionality from the addon, presents a description asking the user to uninstall, and adds a README with some context. A similar set of changes will occur on the AMO page once this is uploaded there.
pull_commit_message:
shut it down

inhuman ads infrastructure was decommissioned almost a year ago. this change removes all functionality from the addon, presents a description asking the user to uninstall, and adds a README with some context. A similar set of changes will occur on the AMO page once this is uploaded there.
